[It is always a good idea have current rabies vaccinations for your
pets and livestock, especially if you or your children are involved
in showing the cattle. And always vaccinate the horses. Rabies
vaccination as prevention from this disease is a very cheap
insurance, especially when you compare it to the worth of your life
or that of a loved one.

Every state has their own rabies law regarding the type of
vaccination used and how often. So please visit your veterinarian. - Mod.TG]
